summary: A basic stand alone Nord 2 Handed Boss
descriptionHtml:
A true Nord warrior. She has Had a hard life and it shows.

 Will level with you from 1 to 100, will not set off traps, she is essential and can be married. She is nude when you meet but will equip her gear when recruited. She will be around Alvor's forge in Riverwood.

 Skyrim is a harsh land and it is hard work just to live, add the fighting, looting, and chasing dragons and the effects should show in how you look. Good drinks, good music, and good friends is all she's ever asked for in life, but she'll kill you if she has to.  Breze has had a hard life and it has left it's mark, but she is always ready for more. Invite her along with you and you will be glad you did.

    Breze picked up her mothers great sword when she was 10 years old and been swinging one ever since. She took to the wild at 15 and lived off the land, her sword and her wit. She's lived off wild game and forest greens, which have left her with a very lean look. Swinging a great sword and mountain living has given her stamina and strength. Her parents and the gods gave her a keen wit and experience has given her great skill and spirit.  Just what the Dragon born needs for those brutal battles ahead.


   This is the largest body that I have at the moment that still looks good.
  Still working on them and will have more larger versions when I can get
  them done, and permissions.

    She has a stand alone custom  UNP body with resources from Tigersan's
diesel body, her hair is from KS Hair Renewal by Kalilies and Stealthic
and she is wearing UNP Spice Gear in the screenshots. Thank you to all
of them for the great resources that make Skyrim a much more pleasant
place to be.
author: wachie61
